    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## 📥 Data Ingestion Pipeline\n\n**Purpose**: Load sales documents into Pinecone vector store\n\n**Process**:\n1. List files from Google Drive (PDFs, Docs, DOCX, TXT, ZIP)\n2. Download each file as binary data\n3. Parse JSON and split content from metadata\n4. Split into 1000-char chunks (200 overlap)\n5. Generate embeddings with OpenAI\n6. Insert into Pinecone with metadata\n\n**Metadata Added**:\n- source: filename\n- mimeType: file type\n- uploadDate: timestamp",
        "height": 420,
        "width": 420,
        "color": 2
      },
      "id": "7e6c94cc-9705-420c-957c-2f62e6749d99",
      "name": "Sticky Note 1",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        48,
        -256
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "content": "## 🔧 Setup Instructions\n\n1. **Google Drive**: Connect OAuth2, select folder with sales docs\n2. **Pinecone**: Create index (dimension: 1536 for text-embedding-3-small)\n3. **OpenAI**: API key for embeddings\n\n**Supported Formats**:\n- PDF, Google Docs, DOCX, TXT, EPUB, CSV, JSON, ZIP\n\n**Run**: Click \"Test workflow\" to process up to 50 files\n\n**For ongoing sync**: Replace Manual Trigger with Google Drive Trigger",
        "height": 280,
        "width": 380,
        "color": 4
      },
      "id": "5e5652ae-7d51-4dff-be13-874c7293117d",
      "name": "Sticky Note 2",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        528,
        -240
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "mode": "runOnceForEachItem",
        "jsCode": "// Get the binary buffer properly through n8n's helper\nconst buffer = await this.helpers.getBinaryDataBuffer(\n  $itemIndex,\n  'data'\n);\n\nconst jsonString = buffer.toString('utf-8');\nconst parsed = JSON.parse(jsonString);\n\nreturn {\n  json: {\n    content: parsed.content,\n    metadata: parsed.metadata,\n    fileName: $input.item.json.name\n  }\n};"
      },
      "id": "61fd863a-46d3-448f-8d80-f456b4fc7c17",
      "name": "Parse JSON and Split",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.code",
      "typeVersion": 2,
      "position": [
        912,
        304
      ]
    },
    {
      "parameters": {
        "resource": "fileFolder",
        "queryString": ".json",
        "limit": 100,
        "filter": {
          "folderId": {
            "__rl": true,
            "value": "1UxC7DRBp_7mGwLGikx8uTgvdIkDkij2a",
            "mode": "list",
            "cachedResultName": "corpus",
            "cachedResultUrl": "https://drive.google.com/drive/folders/1UxC7DRBp_7mGwLGikx8uTgvdIkDkij2a"
          }
        },
        "options": {}
      },
      "id": "0c204026-8f01-4684-b67a-bbb97a1827c9",
      "name": "Search files and folders",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.googleDrive",
      "typeVersion": 3,
